Nacionalni svet invalidskih organizacij Slovenije (NSIOS) as an umbrella organisation represents 21 member associations with over 100.000 individual members.&#xd;
The National Council shall be composed of all the representative and other disabled people's organisations which are the signatories to Memorandum of Association and Activities of the National Council of Disabled People's Organisations of Slovenia. &#xd;
&#xd;
Members:&#xd;
V NSIOS je vključenih 24 nacionalnih invalidskih organizacij. 17 od teh ima status reprezentativnosti za določeno skupino invalidov.&#xd;
